  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    EventDispatcher
    Generic Event Dispatcher Interface.
    EventListener
    Event listener interface.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Event<T>
    Event object.
    EventListenerSet
    The EventListener collection.
    MultiEventListeners  
    MultiListenerEventDispatcher
    Event dispatcher User can use MultiListenerEventDispatcher.addEventListener(Object, EventListener) method to register event and related event listener Invoke MultiListenerEventDispatcher.dispatchEvent(org.ogcs.event.Event) method to dispatch event context to registered event listeners after user's action trigger registered event
    SingleListenerEventDispatcher<T>
    Single listener event dispatcher.
